Helm commands
helm install {unique release name} location of folder: webapp1/v
helm install mywebapp-release webapp1/
‚ï≠‚îÄ ÔÖπ ÓÇ∞ ÔÅº ~/helm-webapp ÓÇ∞   ÓÇ≤ ‚úî ÓÇ≤ at minikube ‚éà ÓÇ≤ at 05:24:07 PM ÔÄó
‚ï∞‚îÄ helm install mywebapp-release webapp1/ --namespace=basic-helm
